summary: Just another preset, this time Enaid, a half breton, half nord.
descriptionHtml:
3rd sibling done, 1 more to go :'(
This one's Enaid, the youngest, he's originally a breton, but he looked ugly as fuck in that race so i tried with nord and had a much better result (still gonna be a breton in the lore lol fight me). Hopefully i'll be able to turn the four siblings into followers once i finish them all.
